{"tid":49244,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"與其整個冇用既filter 不如咁做喇","createTime":"2016-12-21T14:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T02:41:01.000Z","uid":15696,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae30ef185aa1d1bc96c375181ab45384548c1905","tid":49244,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"filter就好似以前高登個D粗囗過濾模式，治標唔治本，其實加emoji係好事，不過今次真係做錯左，唔通你以後整十幾個filter option出黎咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，明明大部分巴絲唔鍾意個emoji，竟然為左少部份人叫其他人開filter，感覺好似係處理出錯左又唔肯認咁，不如徹底整個好啲嘅方案喇。再者，肥絲嘅態度真係好差，好多巴絲眀明理性同佢講野都俾佢串/屌，部分巴絲已經覺得佢好剋人憎，如果連巴再偏幫佢，真係關公災難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個巴打idea其實幾好：不如咁啦，整個本周icon制度 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/48439/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/48439/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n今次攪個公投，決定呢個「試用」左幾日嘅emoji 留唔留低，然後每次加新emoji都咁做，又可以炒熱個post，又可以睇民意，真係win win。<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾我講中，遲D連巴只會加個filter，然後以後都唔會加任何新emoji，完。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318e92079cac6c93b80ab323f023b9834e6b131c","tid":49244,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"bfaee14c6d66d2c789fa0ada7c4e3e6a6d18dc28","tid":49244,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:36:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01186368ea14f2115047c977e1672d88d77f2431","tid":49244,"uid":7240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ad64cf31722487d6b4b5fcd099168413763ec6","tid":49244,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"Agher<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者唔投票整限定icon淨係上架一兩星期<br />\n都好過整幾廿個filter"},{"pid":"feed149d2ab97e39b5d624fbdf9645921731bbd5","tid":49244,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Agher<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者唔投票整限定icon淨係上架一兩星期<br />\n都好過整幾廿個filter</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打錯字，agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44d730d3cd6a5db0af92aba2e484b53ff750bb5","tid":49244,"uid":6221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"其實真心建議唔好玩公投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9925ebcd96a586ccad78b117e2c555b3581f3c","tid":49244,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:41:08.000Z","msg":"其實加新icon係好事黎，以前高登新icon一上都好多人玩，反而好少咁多人反對，其實真係質素同啱唔啱放係forum既問題，如果連巴自己掌握唔到，真係公投算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c7e9e1d6ba487c98d7f1b1193270807448010d","tid":49244,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/d7/Ww_yo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette4.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fd7%2FWw_yo.jpg&h=ee133975&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7e2ac7a479c8444e8718c7100bc9ca91cf5fdd7","tid":49244,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實真心建議唔好玩公投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可能會有兩種結果：一係以後唔再整新icon<br />\n<br />\n一係又再嘈多次，有冇其他方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43544408867a053dd33fb7c055bc6c8a86a98338","tid":49244,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"呢D 理性少少嘅post 佢地係會當睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n所以.......<span style=\"fon